      <title>万达接近达成贷款协议以支付上市前投资者的回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/wanda-nears-deal-for-loan-facility-to-pay-pre-ipo-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，大连万达商业管理集团股份有限公司本周向一些投资者表示，一笔可用于向其旗下某个子公司的部分 IPO 前投资者支付的贷款即将完成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/wanda-nears-deal-for-loan-facility-to-pay-pre-ipo-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:31:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印尼盾兑美元汇率自 5 月以来首次突破 16,000</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rupiah-rises-past-16-000-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元走弱，且印尼官员早前采取措施平息投资者对新政府财政政策的担忧，印尼盾兑美元汇率突破了 16,000 的关键关口。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rupiah-rises-past-16-000-per-dollar-for-first-time-since-may</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:22:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称全球四分之三的套利交易现已平仓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/jpmorgan-says-three-quarters-of-global-carry-trades-now-unwound</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，全球四分之三的套利交易目前已被取消，最近的抛售抹去了今年的涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/jpmorgan-says-three-quarters-of-global-carry-trades-now-unwound</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国解散政党成员誓言与保守派争夺权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/disbanded-thai-party-members-vow-to-battle-old-guards-for-power</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国反对党解散后，其支持者誓言要组建新政党，挑战保守派当权派的权力，这为东南亚第二大经济体的进一步政治动荡埋下了伏笔。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/disbanded-thai-party-members-vow-to-battle-old-guards-for-power</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:01:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金放弃部分日元看涨押注但担心出现大幅波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hedge-funds-ditch-some-bullish-yen-bets-but-fear-of-swings-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对冲基金似乎已撤出对日元最看涨的押注，但在当前水平上，对冲头寸仍需付出高昂代价，这表明日元下一步走势的不确定性增加。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/hedge-funds-ditch-some-bullish-yen-bets-but-fear-of-swings-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:53:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国航空燃油需求激增为炼油商带来罕见提振</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/jet-fuel-demand-spike-in-china-a-rare-bright-spot-for-refiners</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着航班恢复飞行，中国的航空燃料需求正在好转，这为国内炼油商提供了一定支撑，因为他们正努力应对柴油和汽油消费低迷导致的行业压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/jet-fuel-demand-spike-in-china-a-rare-bright-spot-for-refiners</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:53:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券赎回迫在眉睫，乐天亏损或将收窄</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rakuten-likely-to-report-narrower-loss-as-bond-redemptions-loom</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乐天集团公司 (Rakuten Group Inc.) 预计将于周五公布 4 月至 6 月当季亏损收窄，这将增强人们对其偿还明年到期债券能力的信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/rakuten-likely-to-report-narrower-loss-as-bond-redemptions-loom</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 01:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
